name: Listened to Dear Internet Episode 76: Camping Conundrum

content.html:
Dear Internet, We had to record on a different night this week due to scheduling conflicts, and unfortunately Michaels power went out. Luckily though, our pal Jessy from Naruto-reviewto could join us! On this week’s show we talk about drama at the campsite, the hatman, and role playing at work. We would greatly appreciate if you could leave us a 5-star review on your podcast app of choice! If you want more Dear Internet, please consider supporting us on patreon through Dear Internet. Sincerely, The coHosts- Nick, Jennifer, Michael, and Tim Lanning! Apple Podcast, Spotify, RSS – follow us on Twitter!

By Dear Internet
